Here's a function I use everywhere. Is the signature okay?

```ts
export function renderReport(data: ReportData, isSummary: boolean) {
  if (isSummary) {
    return renderSummaryLayout(data);
  }
  return renderDetailLayout(data);
}
```

Callers do `renderReport(d, true)` and `renderReport(d, false)`.

